so... explain to me... if master yi is such a noob champ that can carry by &quot;just rightclicking&quot; as everyone says...
why arent these people playing him?
i literally never saw a master yi in bronze saying &quot;i play yi to get out of bronze. but its my fault that i suck with him&quot;
